      "text": "갇혀있는 상태입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 527.04,
      "end": 529.22,
      "text": "빨리 탈출해야 될 텐데"
    },
    {
      "start": 529.22,
      "end": 530.22,
      "text": "you can do it"
    },
    {
      "start": 530.22,
      "end": 533.08,
      "text": "자 그럼 한 번 더 들어보시죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 533.08,
      "end": 535.8,
      "text": "you wouldn't just throw the ferris wheel at the town"
    },
    {
      "start": 535.8,
      "end": 537.34,
      "text": "well of course not silly"
    },
    {
      "start": 537.34,
      "end": 539.88,
      "text": "I'm gonna roll it in the town"
    },
    {
      "start": 539.88,
      "end": 541.05,
      "text": "what?"
    },
    {
      "start": 541.29,
      "end": 542.49,
      "text": "this will be unforgettable"
    },
    {
      "start": 542.49,
      "end": 544.67,
      "text": "I can't wait to see my name in lights"
    },
    {
      "start": 544.67,
      "end": 546.83,
      "text": "all art requires sacrifice"
    },
    {
      "start": 546.83,
      "end": 549.25,
      "text": "when were you going to tell me about this?"
    },
    {
      "start": 550.03,
      "end": 551.19,
      "text": "how about now?"
    },
    {
      "start": 551.91,
      "end": 553.79,
      "text": "but if you destroy all the homes"
    },
    {
      "start": 553.79,
      "end": 556.15,
      "text": "that means you'll also destroy all the fins"
    },
    {
      "start": 556.15,
      "end": 556.91,
      "text": "remember?"
    },
    {
      "start": 556.91,
      "end": 559.09,
      "text": "not every story has a happy ending"
    },
    {
      "start": 559.09,
      "end": 560.31,
      "text": "and no one's gonna suffer"
